Package org.opt4j.satdecoding

Class SATGenotype

java.lang.Object
org.opt4j.core.genotype.CompositeGenotype<Integer,Genotype>
org.opt4j.satdecoding.SATGenotype
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<Map.Entry<Integer,Genotype>>, Genotype
public class SATGenotype extends CompositeGenotype<Integer,Genotype>
Specialized Genotype for the AbstractSATDecoder. The SATGenotype consists of two components: a binary and a double vector.
